    "comments: false\n",
    "layout: notebook\n",
    "title: Logic Gates With Emojis\n",
    "description: Expanding on the logic gates, this will produce an output containing an emoji\n",
    "type: hacks\n",
    "toc: true\n",
    "courses: { compsci: {week: 1} }\n",
